                :time (i / initial~4)))

            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (g2 / government-organization~8
                :name (n2 / name~8
                    :op1 "House"~8))
            :ARG2 (s2 / speaker~9))
        :manner (v / vote-01~12
            :ARG2 (m2 / majority~11)))
    :snt2 (f / face-01~16
        :ARG0 (h2 / he~14
            :same-as p)
        :ARG1 (t / test-01~19
            :ARG1 h2
            :ARG1-of (m / major-02~18)
            :ARG2 (p2 / prevent-01~21
                :ARG0 h2
                :ARG1 (s / shut-down-05~24
                    :ARG1 (g3 / government-organization~23
                        :ARG0-of (g / govern-01~23)))
                :time (b / by~25
                    :op1 (d / date-entity~26

            :ord (o / ordinal-entity~17
                :quant 1~17))
        :time (n3 / now~15)))
